         <section-body><paragraph-text type="preamble">This place covers:</paragraph-text>
            <paragraph-text type="body">This group includes all means to avoid the propagation of the detonation or blast wave during the destruction of ammunition by controlled detonation in a pressure chamber which is able to withstand a detonation inside. Also includes detonation wave guiding means.</paragraph-text>
